Hey guys! Mark your calendars for June 10th at 5pm, because we are having a fundraiser to raise money for my medical expenses. 💙There will be a silent auction, dessert auction, 2 live auction goodies, a photo booth, snacks, and beverages! There will also be some free giveaway items😊
-
-
I will be speaking and giving my testimony on how I found the cancer, how I'm able to stay strong, how God has impact my life, and how I am able to fight this battle each day and help others. It will be a night full of fun, laughter, love, and excitement💕
-
-
The event will be held in Federal Way, Wa on June 10th at 5pm. For each ticket that is purchased, we ask that you bring 1(or more) canned food item so that it can be donated to charity or a family/person in need. There is only a limited number of tickets available and you can find the link for the tickets in my bio🎟
I truly appreciate all your love and support. It does not go unnoticed at all💕 I love you all and can't wait to see you on June 10th😊😘
